🔗 Music Project out now 🔗
@areainarea x @ambush_official x @gentlemonster 
 
Korea's new wave @hwimmm @groovypark and Ash Island made a song '잡아줄게 (Carabiner) just for this special project. Now out now on all global streaming platforms‼️ 🖤💙

그루비룸의 레이블 에어리어(AREA)가 오늘 새 프로젝트 음원을 공개했습니다. 🙌 애쉬 아일랜드가 참여한 음원 '잡아줄게 (Carabiner)'입니다. 🔗이 곡은앰부쉬x젠틀몬스터의 아이웨어 협업 컬렉션👓 '카라비너(Carabiner)'를 주제로 만든 음악인데요. 지금 유튜브와 음원 사이트에서 감상해보세요! 

#AREA #그루비룸 #groovyroom #휘민 #규정　#gentlemonster #ambush

node.text:
4,843 ACRES of RAINFOREST SAVED @moetchandon x @ambush_official collaboration donation made it possible. 🙏🏽💚🍃
 
As you remember, #moëtchandon pledged to donate a portion of profits from the sale of limited-edition Moët & Chandon x #AMBUSH bottles to the @worldlandtrust – an international conservation charity that protects threatened natural habitats – to help preserve the #Canandé Reserve in the Ecuadorian #Chocó Forest, a place as biodiverse as the Amazon rainforest but far more threatened. The remarkable donation has had a direct impact on stopping the deforestation of the Chocó, not just for the sake of its fragile species but also to combat one of the causes of climate change.
 
I want to take this moment to thank you Moët & Chandon, for making my idea come to life and for everyone who purchased the bottles. You guys' support has contributed to the impact of this noble amazing cause! 

Here's the video from the @WorldLandTrust bout this donation: 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SfrGhur_rzc

MUSHROOM VISIONARIES

What lies beneath the mushroom? These plump, strange, immensely varied spore carriers are in fact just the tip of an organism that is as vast and as deeply complex as the human brain. 

The article is now up on www.ambushdesign.com

node.text:
From @voguekorea 🖤🇰🇷

Repost - 전세계 청춘의 꿈이 된 브랜드 #앰부시(@ambush_official). #보그 9월호에선 앰부시의 수장인 #윤안(@yoon_ambush)와 만났습니다. 그 만남을 기념해 서울의 여덟 모델이 앰부시 2021 가을 컬렉션을 입고 카메라 앞에 섰습니다. 보그가 포착한 청춘의 빛나는 순간을 감상하세요.

fashion editor Kihoh Sohn
film director Hyun Heo

#ambush #voguekorea

node.text:
For Vogue Korea September issue. 🇰🇷🖤

Repost @voguekorea
“이제 패션 디자이너는 벽이나 커튼 뒤에 숨지 않는다. 오디언스는 디자이너와 소통하길 원하기에 하나의 ‘퍼스널리티’가 되어야 한다. 그 균형은 물론 자신에게 맞도록 조절해야 한다.” #보그 9월호를 위해 만난 #앰부시(@ambush_official)의 크리에이티브 디렉터 (@yoon_ambush)는 요즘 시대의 디자이너를 이렇게 정의합니다. 그녀와 나눈 이야기와 한국 남자 모델 8명이 앰부시의 가을 컬렉션을 입고 밤거리를 달린 화보를 지금 보그닷컴(vogue.co.kr)에서 확인하세요.

fashion editor Kihoh Sohn
photographer Jongha Park
portrait Ambush Studio
model Donghyun Kim, Jungwoo Kim, Min Shin, Seungchan Lee, Yugo Takano, Hyunjae Jung, Jinwoo Jang, Jinhee Han
hair Hyunwoo Lee
makeup Heejung Hwang

#AMBUSH #voguekorea #🇰🇷

node.text:
𝗔𝗠𝗕𝗨𝗦𝗛 𝑭𝑰𝑬𝑳𝑫 𝑺𝑻𝑼𝑫𝒀

NIHON NOIR: TOKYO’S OTHERWORLDLY NIGHTSCAPES

In #Tokyo, find skyscrapers and neon lights in a dense, urban landscape that is unlike anywhere else.

Commonplace in #Japan, but once viewed from an outsider point of view, they often seem like scenes from another dimension. Looking from high above on a rooftop, the dense cityscape may make you feel like you are in a completely different world. Fascinated by the sci-fi futurism of Tokyo, photographer Tom Blachford shoots next level images of the city where the past and future come and go.

The article now up on www.ambushdesign.com
⁣
🖊️ @kurumifukutsu / Translated by Sho Mitsui
📸 @blachford
